comments: Redick (PHI) makes marginal contact to the body of Wade (MIA) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Waiters (MIA) briefly engages with Butler (PHI) but does not affect his FOM.
B. Simmons (PHI) maintains his pivot foot on the perimeter.
Marjanovic (PHI) makes marginal contact with Waiters (MIA) as he disengages from the pick.
Winslow (MIA) makes contact to the arm of Marjanovic (PHI) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Redick (PHI) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Wade (MIA).
Marjanovic (PHI) makes marginal contact with Waiters (MIA) as he disengages from the pick.
Wade (MIA) slips the contact and does not dislodge Redick (PHI) from his legally obtained position when he releases the pass.
Winslow (MIA) makes contact to the arm of Marjanovic (PHI) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Butler (PHI) and Wade (MIA) make incidental contact off ball.
Harris (PHI) places two hands around Richardson (MIA) during his drive.
Harris (PHI) establishes possession of the ball in the frontcourt before eight seconds elapses.
